Net-Rovio version 1.0
======================

CHANGES

In 1.0: Switched from WWW::Mechanize to LWP::Request for simplicity, added send_photo()
In 0.9: A second argument for send() is optional
In 0.8: Prerequisite for WWW::Mechanize added

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::Request

